Uses of Package
joelib2.io

Packages that use joelib2.io
joelib2.algo Provides classes for calculating Depth First Search (DFS) [] Breadth First Search (BFS) [] on molecular graphs. 
joelib2.algo.datamining.weka Provides classes for an interface to the Weka Data Mining library. 
joelib2.algo.morgan Provides classes for Morgan number generation and unique molecule numbering. 
joelib2.example Provides testing classes for processing molecular data. 
joelib2.feature Provides classes for defining molecular properties (descriptors). 
joelib2.feature.data Provides classes for building descriptor matrices. 
joelib2.feature.result Provides representating classes for molecular properties (descriptors). 
joelib2.feature.types.atompair   
joelib2.gui.util   
joelib2.io Provides classes for defining molecular import and export methods. 
joelib2.io.types Provides representating classes for the molecular import and export methods. 
joelib2.io.types.cml Provides helper classes for processing the Chemical Markup Language (CML) [, , , , , ]. 
joelib2.math.similarity   
joelib2.molecule Provides classes for molecular data structures. 
joelib2.molecule.types Provides classes for atom and bond properties. 
joelib2.process.types Provides representating classes for the molecular processing methods. 
joelib2.ring Provides classes for finding the Smallest Set of Smallest Rings (SSSR) []. 
joelib2.util Provides all kind of additional technical/molecular helper classes. 
joelib2.util.database
